replies.body:
I'm not all ping t-t.  Low ms helps, but I can beat people without low ms as well. I have other tactics, even if I do start lagging. It's also aim, even though those were warm-ups.

 If I have the same ms as someone and they have better aim than me, it's the equivalent of them having 5-10ms lower than me.
